	\textbf{Requires:} Collective
	
	\textbf{Cost:} +1 Willpower
	
	The noble reweaves the threads that bind an organisation together to include herself. When she uses Collective on an organisation large enough to have a Status Merit she gains the Blessing Condition adding half her Terra (rounding up) in Status to an organisation. This organisation cannot be supernatural in nature (which includes any organisation that offers a supernatural Merit or Endowment as a benefit to members). In addition to Status the Princess knows how to talk and act like a member of the organisation, and if she has appropriate Charms (such as Phantom) she knows how to create accurate markers of identity. However her membership is fragile, she will need to come up with her own reasons for why nobody has met her before and if she gives people a reason to investigate her membership they will discover the truth. 
	\end{myindentpar}
	
