    \emph{Success:} Any object with a Durability equal or lesser than the nominated durability becomes transparent to the Princesses eyes. She can see through it but still remains aware of it's shape and general location. If she focuses her attention on an object it solidifies to her eyes, this Charm imposes no perception penalties. If the Princess wishes to look through several objects at once, such as a wardrobe and the wall behind the wardrobe, she must be able to see through their combined durability. 
	
	X-Ray vision provides no advantages to penetrating supernatural concealment or seeing into Twilight, but if the Princess has some other way of doing either it stacks with X-Ray vision.

    \emph{Exceptional Success:}  No extra benefit.\end{myindentpar}

