\subsubsection*{Love's Beacon (Learn \textbullet, Fuoco \textbullet)}

\noindent \textbf{Action:} Instant and resisted, Presence + Empathy - target's Resolve

\noindent \textbf{Cost:} 1 Wisp

\noindent \textbf{Duration:} instant \\ 

