The Princess cannot, however, speak any human language except the Royal Tongue unless the animal is able to mimic human speech (like a parrot); she takes penalties on any task that calls for hands, unless the animal has them (like a monkey) or capable manipulators (an octopus' tentacles); and her Regalia are transformed away and unavailable. Finally, any object she picked up after transforming out of mundane form does not change with her.

The Princess subtracts the difference between her normal Size and the animal's Size from the activation roll when using the Charm. She may remain in beast form as long as she can remain transformed normally, and may end the Charm at any time with a standard transformation roll or by returning to mundane form. The bonuses or penalties for Size provided by the Charm Royal Stature do not apply, it is assumed that the base attributes for an animal will take into account it's size. 

