	The Princess may attack others by rolling Strength + Lacrima, she does Lethal damage but a successful attack also drains a point of Willpower. She may also speak as normal, her strange form grants a Lacrima bonus to Intimidation. The Princess also has all the Benefits of the Darkened Template, but she uses the Noble rules for Sensitivity. 

