If the Princess has a Resolve + Tempesta of 5 or more, she is immune to any Taint Curses that affect her behaviour directly, such as Tainted Vice. At a Resolve + Tempesta of 10 or more she can comfortably survive in the Dark World, though she gains no protection from the many more active dangers in that physical hell.

