\subsubsection*{Choke It Down (Restore \textbullet\textbullet\textbullet, Tempesta \textbullet\textbullet)}

\noindent \textbf{Action:} Instant, unrolled

\noindent \textbf{Cost:} 2 Wisps, 1 resistant Lethal or Aggravated damage \\

